00:41:21.990 --> 00:41:27.860
Unless, hm, could you write
it at a different time,

00:41:27.860 --> 00:41:31.230
year 605 of the Caka era began
on the fifth day of the waning

00:41:31.230 --> 00:41:31.730
moon?

00:41:31.730 --> 00:41:34.470
Maybe they're talking like we
