00:41:34.470 --> 00:41:37.880
Something happened on a
certain-- yeah, it could be.

00:41:37.880 --> 00:41:40.160
But the temple was
built around that time.

00:41:40.160 --> 00:41:41.890
It's a seventh century temple.

00:41:41.890 --> 00:41:43.840
The styles are seventh century.

00:41:43.840 --> 00:41:45.430
And Hab Touch
himself is actually

00:41:45.430 --> 00:41:49.000
an expert on Cambodian art.

00:41:49.000 --> 00:41:52.690
And he actually has classified
the Cambodian art styles

00:41:52.690 --> 00:41:54.810
into five different styles.

00:41:54.810 --> 00:41:59.390
And the style of Sambor-- there
are two Sambors, by the way.

00:41:59.390 --> 00:42:00.950
And for several
months, I was going

00:42:00.950 --> 00:42:04.580
to the wrong Sambor trying
to look for it years before.

00:42:04.580 --> 00:42:09.380
There's a Sambor that's near
